    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cassettes of audiotape. According to international standards, the tape is usually 0.15 inches (3.8 millimetres) wide and can carry 4 to 8 tracks.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
